13:
Oh-ho! Nicely done, boys. That's 
almost all of 'em.
18: Why did we bring him along again?
22:
Forget about him. We can handle this 
on our—
31:
Heh-heh! Now that's how you kill three 
birds with one stone!
32:
...Sure you oughta be lookin' this way? 
You'd better finish your plate first!
44:
Mm, MMM! That's goooood eatin'. 
Nothin' like a hot meal after a hard 
day's work!
50:
Hey, don't sweat the small stuff. You'll 
make the booze taste bad.
55:
...Booze?
You do realize that our quest isn't over 
yet, right?!
59:
No need to be upset because you were 
slow! Everyone has off days, right?
61:
Besides! Just leftovers to clean up 
after this, yeah? Might as well have 
a celebratory drink! Am I right, 
Nimbus?
66:
I'm good.
If I wanted to play a drunkard, 
I wouldn't need props.
69:
...Yeah? And what's that supposed to 
mean?
73: Er, um... L-Light! You want some?
89:
Ahaha... AHAHAHA! You thought you 
could escape from us, Vyron?
Or should I say... Velgar Solon!
90:
After all this time... You're still tryin' to 
cover for her?!
92:
Damn you... I'll show you how it feels to 
have everything taken from you!
103: ...Heh. My aim ain't what it used to be
105:
Guess my age is finally catchin' up to 
me, huh?
115:
So you're running away again.
Afraid that you're gonna cause trouble 
for us?
122:
Heh. What happened to your usual 
cheer and bravado?
128:
You piss me off sometimes, you know 
that? We never asked for you to be our 
protector.
130:
It might be hard for you to believe, but 
we can look after our own fine here.
132: Oh yeah? How'd that work out for you?
135:
Do you remember what she looked like 
when she laughed?
138:
I've fought so many battles since... 
I can barely remember it.
151:
If you wish to run, you're free to do so. 
But if you plan on doing something 
reckless...
169:
Heh... Ahahaha! Now I've seen 
everything!
176:
If you're so keen on protectin' 
someone, you can start with Stella 
here.
178:
I mean, even your drunken self is 
capable of wipin' someone's ass, right?
182:
I'm perfectly capable of doing that 
much myself.
184:
Fine, you got me. I ain't goin' anywhere 
anytime soon, so take it easy.
186:
Heh... It's been a while since anyone's 
looked at me with eyes like that.
